# Vietnamese Eden MVP — Cursor AI Instructions

## Project Context

- **Repo**: vietnamese-eden-mvp (Next.js 14 App Router + TypeScript strict + Tailwind + shadcn/ui + Supabase)
- **Prototype UI repo**: s-ng-t-o-vi-t (TanStack Start + Vite 7 + React 19 + Tailwind 4 + shadcn/ui)
- **Decision**: Không phát triển song song 2 repo. Dùng prototype làm nguồn tham khảo UI, port từng page/component sang production repo. Không port framework TanStack.

## Stack

- Next.js 14 App Router
- TypeScript (strict)
- Tailwind CSS v3
- shadcn/ui (đã cài đầy đủ primitives)
- Supabase (auth + database)
- Lucide React icons

## Database Schema (10 bảng)

- `workspaces`, `boards`, `content_items`, `board_content_items` (many-to-many), `content_analyses`, `voice_profiles`, `generated_outputs`, `content_calendar_items`, `subscriptions`, `users` (via Supabase Auth)

## Auth

- Supabase Auth với middleware.ts bảo vệ route `/dashboard/*`
- Protected routes tự động redirect nếu chưa login

## Port Strategy

1. Foundation: `AppShell` + `AppSidebar` layout
2. Pages: `dashboard` → `boards` → `board detail`
3. Features: `AddContentModal` (text + URL)
4. Milestones sau: Breakdown (M3), Voice (M4), Remix (M5), Calendar (M6), Landing (M7)

## CSS Tokens cần dùng

```css
/* Tailwind extensions */
--brand: #8B5CF6;
--brand-2: #A78BFA;
--brand-3: #C4B5FD;
--brand-4: #DDD6FE;

/* Classes custom */
bg-gradient-brand: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B5CF6, #A78BFA);
shadow-glow: 0 4px 20px rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.3);
shadow-card: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
font-display: Inter or system display font;
```

## Quy tắc code

- TypeScript strict: không dùng `any`
- Server Components mặc định, chỉ dùng `"use client"` khi cần interactivity
- Supabase queries qua Server Actions hoặc `supabase/ssr` helpers
- shadcn/ui primitives đã có — dùng `npx shadcn add <component>` nếu thiếu
- Tiếng Việt cho toàn bộ UI copy
- `npm run lint && npm run type-check && npm run build` phải pass trước khi commit
